        <scopecontent id="ref2">
            <head>Scope and Contents</head>
            <p>Return of the brigade commanded by Brigadier General James Clinton at White Plains, N.Y. during the Revolutionary War. The return is dated July 18, 1778.</p>
        </scopecontent>
        <accessrestrict id="ref1">
